citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:55 AM on
12/6/2024. The inspector contacted the licensee by phone and was told that there was no person available to conduct a
facility inspection. Failure to provide access to the facility, animals, and records for inspection is a violation of the AWA
and regulations. Failure to comply may result in enforcement action.
End Section
